high_descs: Turn right, go across the room, turn right and go behind the counter on the right.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, go across the room and turn left to the fridge.
Put the knife in the cup inside the freezer.
Pick up the cup with the knife inside it.
Turn left, go across the room and turn right toward the sink.
Put the cup on the counter by the left corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then hang a right and walk over to the sink, turn right and walk forward then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the butter knife off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the butter knife inside the glass in the upper compartment.
Pick up the glass with the butter knife in it out of the fridge, then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the glass with the butter knife in it on the front edge of the counter in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Make a right to walk around the kitchen island, stopping to face it.
Pick up the knife from the counter of the kitchen island.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Put the knife in a glass that is in the freezer.
Take the glass with the knife in it out of the freezer.
Make a left to walk towards the sink.
Set the glass and knife down on the countertop in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife from the counter into a glass from the freezer to set them near the sink.
